column4: The awarded loans will settle on July 30, 2009, and will mature on August 27, 2009. The stop-out rate shown above will apply to all awarded loans.
column5: Institutions that submitted winning bids will be contacted by their respective Reserve Banks by 11:30 a.m. EDT on July 28, 2009. Participants have until 12:30 p.m. EDT on July 28, 2009, to inform their local Reserve Bank of any error.
